  "content": "<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Once unlocked, the student must decide immediately, still unaware of the full consequences.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> A Counter-Faust option exists—another student can attempt to cancel the bargain (but at a cost).</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📖</font> How to Unlock the Faustian Bargain</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><object><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; direction: ltr\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Trigger Condition</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>How the Bargain Appears</div>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>A student reaches a certain XP threshold.</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>The Bargain manifests as a whispered offer.</div>",
